lastCommitMessage: Update agora_market_dart_sdk reference and enhance shipping options management
- Updated agora_market_dart_sdk dependency reference in pubspec.yaml and pubspec.lock to a new commit hash for consistency.
- Refactored shipping options handling in ProductPurchaseConfirmPage to improve address selection and synchronization with user addresses.
- Introduced caching for product shipping options to optimize performance and reduce redundant processing.
- Enhanced the user interface for selecting shipping options, providing clearer feedback and improved usability.
